Before to install fakeProfile on Discord and Vesktop, you need download this:
- Git: https://git-scm.com/downloads
- Node.JS: https://nodejs.org/en
- pnpm: we will do it by npm in proccess

After downloaded these thing we first need to download our Vencord Dev, you need do next:
- `git clone https://github.com/Vendicated/Vencord.git && cd Vencord && npm i -g pnpm && pnpm i`(please write this command in Documents/ folder for example, or folders which you can reach easily)
- After this we do this next command: `cd src && mkdir userplugins && git clone https://github.com/gujarathisampath/fakeProfile.git && pnpm build`
- Well done, now we have Vencord Dev and fakeProfile plugin together!

To inject it on Discord App, you need do this command: `pnpm inject` and choose installed Discord path. If you have opened DIscord you need close it fully by icon in your desktop bar.
To load our Vencord into Vesktop you need do next: Go to Settings -> Vesktop Settings -> Scroll down until you'll find thing named "Vencord Location" -> Choose `dist/` folder from your Vencord Dev folder and done. You can restart it to apply it at all.
